Waking_Up_in_Reno http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Waking_Up_in_Reno 0 Waking Up in Reno is a 2002 American road comedy-drama film directed by Jordan Brady and starring Natasha Richardson, Billy Bob Thornton, Patrick Swayze, and Charlize Theron. The screenplay by Brent Briscoe and Mark Fauser focuses on two redneck couples taking a road trip from Little Rock to Reno to see a monster truck rally.
